import React from 'react';
import { useState} from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';

function MyForm() {
    return(
        < main >
            <
            h1 > MedLab Registration Form < /h1> <
            form >
            <
            label >
            First Name:
            <
            input type = "text"
        name = "first_name" / >
            <
            /label> <br/ > < br / >
            <
            label >
            Last Name:
            <
            input type = "text"
        name = "last_name" / >
            <
            /label> <br/ > < br / >
            <
            label >
            Email:
            <
            input type = "email"
        name = "email" / >
            <
            /label> <br/ > < br / >
            <
            label >
            Phone Number:
            <
            input type = "tel"
        name = "phone" / >
            <
            /label> <br/ > < br / >
            <
            label >
            Address:
            <
            input type = "text"
        name = "address1" / >
            <
            /label> <
            label >
            Address line 2:
            <
            input type = "text"
        name = "address2" / >
            <
            /label> <br/ > < br / >
            <
            label >
            City:
            <
            input type = "text"
        name = "city" / >
            <
            /label> <br/ > < br / >
            <
            label >
            State:
            <
            input type = "text"
        name = "state" / >
            <
            /label> <br/ > < br / >
            <
            label >
            Zip code:
            <
            input type = "number"
        name = "zip" / >
            <
            /label> <br/ > < br / >
            <
            input type = "submit"
        value = "Next" / >
            <
            /form> <
            /main>
    )
}

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
 (<MyForm/>)
);
